name: What do you want to do?
Demon
note:
<raceDesc:
Also known as the cave goblin, it is a subspecies of goblin.
They have high intelligence and can handle weapons and
tools. Their HP is relatively low, but they often appear in
groups.
>

name: Human
note:
<raceDesc:
A common human tribe widely distributed throughout the
continent. They have high intelligence and use weapons,
tools, and various skills. They have no weaknesses, but also
no special resistances.
>

name: Animal
note:
<raceDesc:
A wild beast with a ferocious temperament. It excels in
physical strength and skill, and has high attack power. Most
bad states are effective.
>

name: Magic Creature
note:
<raceDesc:
Magically moving creatures with the physical body of an
object, and are immune to many physical bad statuses. Bad
Status Resistance: [Weak Poison, Strong Poison, Corrosion,
Sleep].]
>

name: Undead
note:
<raceDesc:
Undead that moves around with a dead body. Has high HP.
Immune to physical/mental bad states. Weakness attribute:
[Holy]. Resistance attribute: [Darkness]. BS resistance:
[Weak Poison, Strong Poison, Corrosion, Charm, Sleep,
Curse].]
>

name: Spirit
note:
<raceDesc:
A hollow existence consisting only of soul or spirit. It is
immune to physical attacks and bad status effects on the
body/mind. Weakness: [Holy]. Resistance: [Physical, Dark].
Bad Status Resistance: [Weak Poison, Strong Poison,
Corrosion, Charm, Sleep, Stun, Curse].]
>

name: Ghost
note:
<raceDesc:
Stray spirits that have separated from the flow of the
earth's veins for some reason. They have strong resistance
to specific attributes.
>

name: Plant
note:
<raceDesc:
From the earth's veins flow spirits with willpower that
imbue trees and plants. They can use magic, but are slow and
weak against flames. Weakness attribute: [Flame] Resistance
attribute: [Wind] BS resistance: [Stun].]
>

name: Slime
note:
<raceDesc:
Mysterious creature of unknown origin. Weakness attribute:
[Flame] Resistance attribute: [Water] BS resistance: [Stun,
Weak Poison, Severe Poison]]
>

name: Insect
note:
<raceDesc:
Insects that breed in adapted places. They may have poison
or a hard shell. Their HP is relatively low. Weakness
attribute: [Ice].]
>

name: Crustacean
note:
<raceDesc:
A creature with a hard shell. It has high defense and is
difficult to damage. Weakness attribute: [Thunder].]
>

name: Rastian
note:
<raceDesc:
Rustium creatures. They are also known as residents of the
Lewd World. Weakness attribute: [Ice].]
>

name: Fish
note:
<raceDesc:
A monster that mainly operates underwater. There is no
chance of winning if you are dragged into the water.
Weakness attribute: [Thunder] Resistance attribute: [Water].]
>

name: Dragon
note:
<raceDesc:
Primitive creatures that directly use spirits as their
energy source. They are capable of releasing powerful
breaths of specific attributes and have strong resistance to
certain attributes. Weakness attribute: [Holy] Resistance
attributes: [Physical, Dark] BS resistance: [Stun, Bind,
Curse]]
>
